topics.body:
Hey guys what's up with all of the pics of Cobra? 

Also I've got some new stuff I'm working on for a fanfic, well not so new. I just had no idea how to make this particular pic work. Take it from me, trying to research international policies and foreign relations isn't easy, its flipping hard. 

I'm currently trying to make a fanfic where America is going through the economic financial crisis, during this time they manage to open up a rift in time and space to another reality which is where Equestria is, and well things kind of go from there. 

But I really don't know how to make things sound, realistic, I mean what would the actual US government do when it opens a portal to another reality? Would they invade it once they discover sizable amounts of resources? 

Equestria has plenty by the looks of the show, Rarity digs up gems in the cartloads, so there's plenty of minerals, and if there's oil and coal, its likely that its mostly untouched. So that makes it a lot more fair game. 

Oh and don't forget, there's a certain amount of land, I mean I made the entire continent three times the size of North America, so there's that. I'm sure the US government wouldn't mind taking a chance at procuring more land for agriculture and expansion.

So yeah, this is probably going to end about as well as the colonization of America, if I do this in the manner where the US government is a giant douche.
